OL,3,CDedicated police taskforce launched to
OL,4,Ctackle rise in shoplifting
OL,6,FA dedicated police taskforce has been
OL,7,Fset up in response to a rise in
OL,8,Fshoplifting and other related crime in
OL,9,FScotland.
OL,11,FThe retail crime taskforce includes 14
OL,12,Funiformed officers and detectives who
OL,13,Fwill operate in Edinburgh, Glasgow and
OL,14,FLanarkshire, which experience the
OL,15,Fhighest levels of such offences.
