OL,3,CDedicated police taskforce launched to
OL,4,Ctackle rise in shoplifting
OL,6,FFunded with #3 million from the
OL,7,FScottish government, the taskforce
OL,8,Fwill support other police units in
OL,9,Ftheir actions to prevent retail crime,
OL,10,Fas well as helping shops protect their
OL,11,Fpremises against criminals.
OL,13,FThe team also includes four civilian
OL,14,Fstaff, including specialists analysis.
OL,16,FIt will target repeat offenders by
OL,17,Fusing analytical data and intelligence
OL,18,Fto carry out "proactive" enforcement
OL,19,Fin the most heavily affected areas.
