OL,4,Ctackle rise in shoplifting
OL,6,FHave you heard our podcast Talking
OL,7,FPolitics? Tom, Robert and Anushka dig
OL,8,Finto the biggest issues dominating the
OL,9,Fpolitical agenda in every episode...
OL,11,FLaunching the taskforce, Assistant
OL,12,FChief Constable Tim Mairs said: "There
OL,13,Fis no justification for retail crime
OL,14,Fand the theft of goods from stores, or
OL,15,Fthe harassment and intimidation of
OL,16,Femployees, is certainly not victimless.
OL,18,F"When such offences take place, it can
OL,19,Fhave a significant impact on retail
OL,20,Fworkers, who then feel unsafe at their
OL,21,Fplace of work. This is not acceptable.
