OL,3,CDedicated police taskforce launched to
OL,4,Ctackle rise in shoplifting
OL,6,F"The establishment of the retail crime
OL,7,Ftaskforce demonstrates our commitment
OL,8,Fto working alongside key partners and
OL,9,Fthe retail sector to both prevent
OL,10,Fretail crime occurring, but to conduct
OL,11,Fthorough and professional enforcement
OL,12,Factivity to identify those responsible
OL,13,Fwhenever it does arise."
OL,15,FPolice Scotland explained that the
OL,16,Ftaskforce will work alongside a
OL,17,F"range" of stakeholders to deliver a
OL,18,F"four-strand approach to tackling
OL,19,Fretail crime ` prevent, pursue,
OL,20,Fprotect and prepare".
