OL,6,FCommunity safety minister Siobhian
OL,7,FBrown welcomed the establishment of
OL,8,Fthe taskforce, which she said had been
OL,9,F"enabled" by additional Scottish
OL,10,Fgovernment funding.
OL,12,FShe said this is in addition to a
OL,13,Frecord investment of #1.62 billion for
OL,14,Fpolicing ` up #70 million on 2024-25.
