OL,3,CDedicated police taskforce launched to
OL,4,Ctackle rise in shoplifting
OL,6,F"Retail crime causes significant harm
OL,7,Fand disruption to individuals and
OL,8,Fbusinesses, and I am pleased that this
OL,9,Ftaskforce will work to prevent this
OL,10,Ftype of crime from occurring and to
OL,11,Fensure that when it does happen,
OL,12,Fperpetrators are brought to justice,"
OL,13,FMs Brown added.
OL,15,FLucy Brown, chairwoman of the Scottish
OL,16,FRetail Strategy Industry Leadership
OL,17,FCouncil, said: "While we all know
OL,18,Fthere's no silver bullet to resolve
OL,19,Fretail crime, we are very pleased to
OL,20,Fbe here today to support the launch of
OL,21,Fthis new investment.
